item.description:
Please note that the workshop is now at capacity. Those currently registered are all set to attend.

What does backpacking and cycle touring have in common? More than you think! Join us for an educational weekend exploring the ins and outs of both sports. Learn about trip planning, personal and group gear, food/nutrition, and Leave No Trace principles. Trips for both sports will occur throughout the spring, summer and fall with registration preference given to series attendees. Option for lodging available, $15/night. Workshop fee for Non-AMC members $5. Registration required.
